soldiers charged thousands of protesters in the 
georgian capital early sunday and at least 16 people were killed 
in a crushing melee of clubs shovels sticks and stones official 
sources and activists said 
they threw themselves on our people like beasts and our 
people couldnt do anything said leda archvadze in a telephone 
