the college market has proven a tricky one for some major 
publishers 
newsweek and mcgrawhill co each discontinued magazines aimed 
specifically at college students last year whittle itself dropped 
its flagship campus voice magazine last year and now publishes 
sponored posters under the campus voice name at colleges 
